{"tid":368124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於公屋內施手術非法墮胎 七旬內地助產士囚17個月","createTime":"2017-08-21T10:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T15:27:42.000Z","uid":136994,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f68450435f3965e7480dc1edbea2193d18a05112","tid":368124,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170821/57109166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170821%2F57109166&d=biIZRnvTm2I3mxlUt7lj35ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ffb38b1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170821%2F57109166&h=752ef970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170821/57109166</a><br />\n<br />\n在內地任助產士逾30年的老婦早年來港定居後，於結業診所拿走一批手術工具，繼而透過註冊中醫任中介人，於其自住公屋「操刀」進行墮胎手術。中醫及老婦今早承認兩項串謀意圖促致他人流產罪，法官認同兩被告一生經歷不少困境，但不能忽略兩人於本案因為金錢而完全置病人安危不理，在公屋單位這樣簡陋及衛生差的環境進行手術，一旦病人發生突發意外，兩被告根本沒有措施施救。而且兩被告在事前根本沒有任何口頭警告給病人，不但是嚴重醫療疏忽，兩被告的想法「無知」、「瘋狂」，分別判兩人入獄10個月及17個月。<br />\n<br />\n首被告為註冊女中醫盧煥儀（65歲），次被告為無業婦李淑芬（75歲），兩人於前年一次警方的放蛇行動中被捕，據放蛇女警透露，動手術的公屋環境簡陋，客廳有一張以兩個矮身文件櫃、木板及膠墊搭成的「手術台」，工具僅以壓力煲「消毒」。<br />\n<br />\n首被告向法官呈上前病人撰寫的求情信，指她是一名關心病人的中醫師，次被告的大狀則透露次被告於1960年在內地成為助產士，之後成為「婦科醫生」，有替病人墮胎的經驗；她其後經歷文化大革命，輾轉來到香港，因經濟困難故經營非法墮胎賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n法官考慮兩被告的參與程度，認為首被告是負責拉客，判囚10個月；次被告負責預備及進行手術，罪責較重，判囚17個月。<br />\n<br />\n協助他人非法墮胎比衝立法會仲要輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c86d63c967b210c2e25260b65ca70b41b7e9e","tid":368124,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線"},{"pid":"a9c7ba9583b9784c2d9365146c6adac05f987fac","tid":368124,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:13:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在公屋單位這樣簡陋及衛生差的環境</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4353e6e708a8d3897e0aacb0a6f606850ec38b7e","tid":368124,"uid":108029,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:15:20.000Z","msg":"餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6936219238d6d14ce520e9cc960f58a4b7f3626f","tid":368124,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"判刑過輕，墮胎=殺人。"},{"pid":"d5a4f96bccffdb01266ebe65cbf91f4194398b76","tid":368124,"uid":75137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好以為好新奇  睇佢地個年紀  可能喺九龍城寨做做開"},{"pid":"89756bba52acb886a83690b4db505f0afd49fb8a","tid":368124,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6173b0e0400ff9b1da073a99a96ff1db50394c","tid":368124,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁先10個月"},{"pid":"bf5a9fb8263c0634bd816f680e1257b20ecf4c04","tid":368124,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"間公屋呢?濫用公屋唔駛踢走?"},{"pid":"f07ce8225c96316f7073bf0939beecd174f3235b","tid":368124,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間公屋呢?濫用公屋唔駛踢走?</blockquote><br />\n專才有黨照住"},{"pid":"38c8bd21fe60a27c10341cd8c0b4130796451299","tid":368124,"uid":18233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間公屋呢?濫用公屋唔駛踢走?</blockquote><br />\n